Week 5 - First meeting with client


Key Notes of the meeting
- The client and us are on the same page for what we want from this project
- Meetings will be around every 2 weeks
- We will use macro models as a part of our algortihms to try to predict stock movements
- The language used will be Python

Objectives for Capstone:

First Steps:
- Creating a web scrapper for 3 financials newspaper (The Economist, Financial Times and The Wall Street Journal) to gain insight on intraday macro movements
- Implement a CAPM (Capital Asset Model) to track expected return versus risks as our first model in our algorithm
- Set Up the API for Interactive Brokers

   
